OL,3,CPolice launch forensic review of
OL,4,Cmurders 30 years after family killed
OL,5,Cin fire
OL,7,FPolice believe modern forensic
OL,8,Ftechniques could solve the murders of
OL,9,Fa young mother and her two children,
OL,10,Fwho died when a blaze engulfed their
OL,11,Fhome 30 years ago.
OL,13,FDiane Jones, 21, and her daughters
OL,14,FShauna Hibberd, aged two, and Sarah-
OL,15,FJane Hibberd, aged 13 months, were
OL,16,Fkilled in the fire in the Gurnos,
OL,17,FMerthyr Tydfil, after petrol was
OL,18,Fpoured through their letterbox in
OL,19,FOctober 1995.
