OL,3,CPolice launch forensic review of
OL,4,Cmurders 30 years after family killed
OL,5,Cin fire
OL,7,FTwo women were found guilty of arson
OL,8,Fin 1997 but later had their
OL,9,Fconvictions quashed and, three decades
OL,10,Fon, the murders remain unsolved.
OL,12,FBut South Wales Police hope advances
OL,13,Fin forensic technology could provide a
OL,14,Flong-awaited breakthrough in the case,
OL,15,Fwith the force's Major Crime Review
OL,16,FUnit announcing a forensic review of
OL,17,Fthe murders. Police are also issuing a
OL,18,Ffresh appeal for new information about
OL,19,Fwhat happened.
