OL,3,CPolice launch forensic review of
OL,4,Cmurders 30 years after family killed
OL,5,Cin fire
OL,7,FThe family were found dead in the
OL,8,Fupstairs bedroom of their three-
OL,9,Fbedroom end-of-terrace house on
OL,10,FOctober 11, 1995.
OL,12,FMs Jones' sister Mary Jones has
OL,13,Fdescribed how her life was "shattered
OL,14,Finto a million pieces" after the
OL,15,Ftragedy and said her father, John,
OL,16,Ftook his own life in 2003 after
OL,17,Fstruggling with the loss of his
OL,18,Fdaughter and granddaughters.
OL,20,FDiane's mother Myra has also died
OL,21,Fwithout getting to see justice.
