OL,3,CPolice launch forensic review of
OL,4,Cmurders 30 years after family killed
OL,5,Cin fire
OL,7,FMary Jones said: "It has been 30 years
OL,8,Fbut as a family we are still living
OL,9,Fthis nightmare as if it only happened
OL,10,Fyesterday.
OL,12,F"We didn't just lose a sister and our
OL,13,Fnieces, we also lost our parents. It
OL,14,Fabsolutely broke their hearts and they
OL,15,Fwere never the same.
OL,17,F"As a family we will never give up
OL,18,Ffighting for justice. My mam and dad
OL,19,Fdidn't get to see justice but I'm
OL,20,Fhoping I will for them."
