OL,5,Cin fire
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Gareth
OL,8,FDavies said: "At the time, this tragic
OL,9,Fcase which claimed the innocent lives
OL,10,Fof a mother and her two children sent
OL,11,Fshockwaves through Gurnos and has cast
OL,12,Fa shadow over the community ever since.
OL,14,F"Diane's family have been left without
OL,15,Fanswers for decades and have suffered
OL,16,Fimmeasurably as a result.
