OL,3,CPolice launch forensic review of
OL,4,Cmurders 30 years after family killed
OL,5,Cin fire
OL,7,F"Officers re-examining this case are
OL,8,Fhopeful that new forensic technology
OL,9,Fand techniques which were not
OL,10,Favailable previously will present
OL,11,Fopportunities to progress the
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"Our hope is that we can uncover new
OL,15,Fevidence which will give us the
OL,16,Fbreakthrough we need to find who was
OL,17,Fresponsible."
